Class ProtocolParsing.FastParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nashua.tt151.libraries.parsers.ProtocolParsing.FastParser
  • Enclosing class:
    ProtocolParsing

    public static class ProtocolParsing.FastParser
extends Object
    This class parses FastFormat messages transmitted to and from robot/laptop. The FastFormat uses 1 byte for the header and the rest being a value/args. For more information on FastFormat go to http://goo.gl/S8fwa
    Version:
    0.1 (Indev - unstable)
    Author:
    Brennan Ringey
